                repair cost can vary, but replacing a heating element is often a
                cost-effective way to extend the life of your oven. This repair
                typically doesn't require extensive labor and can be completed
                relatively quickly.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content__page-desc">
              <h3>Temperature Sensor</h3>
