                results. Replacing a malfunctioning convection fan can fix these
                issues and improve cooking consistency. This repair is common in
                convection ovens and usually involves replacing the fan motor.
                The repair cost can vary, but it is generally a worthwhile
                investment to ensure your oven performs at its best.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content__page-desc">
